os - Name - Aprevalia Baill.|website=www.tropicos.org}}</ref><ref>http://www.amjbot.org/content/92/8/1359.full</ref> A number of species such as ''[[Commiphora aprevalii]]'' (Baill.) Guillaumin, were named to commemorate him.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theplantlist.org/tpl1.1/record/kew-2733408|title=Commiphora aprevalii (Baill.) Guillaumin — The Plant List|website=www.theplantlist.org}}</ref>
