'''''Nouvelles Mythologies''''' is a collection of 57 texts written by authors, journalists and editorialists under the direction of [[Jérôme Garcin]] and published in 2007 at [[Éditions du Seuil]] to celebrate the 50th anniversary of the publication of the essay ''[[Mythologies (book)|Mythologies]]'' by [[Roland Barthes]].
